{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idb64ca41b-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s300j–22"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"300j–22"},"text":"§ 300j–22.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Recall of drinking water coolers with lead-lined tanks","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"For purposes of the Consumer Product Safety Act [","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s2051"},"text":"15 U.S.C. 2051","children":[],"tail":" et seq.], all drinking water coolers identified by the Administrator on the list under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s300j–23"},"text":"section 300j–23 of this title","children":[],"tail":" as having a lead-lined tank shall be considered to be imminently hazardous consumer products within the meaning of section 12 of such Act ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s2061"},"text":"15 U.S.C. 2061","children":[],"tail":"). After notice and opportunity for comment, including a public hearing, the Consumer Product Safety Commission shall issue an order requiring the manufacturers and importers of such coolers to repair, replace, or recall and provide a refund for such coolers within 1 year after "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1988-10-31"},"text":"October 31, 1988","children":[],"tail":". For purposes of enforcement, such order shall be treated as an order under section 15(d) of that Act ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s2064/d"},"text":"15 U.S.C. 2064(d)","children":[],"tail":")."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idb64ca41c-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1944-07-01/ch373"},"text":"July 1, 1944, ch. 373","children":[],"tail":", title XIV, § 1462, as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/572/s2/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–572, § 2(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1988-10-31"},"text":"Oct. 31, 1988","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/102/2885"},"text":"102 Stat. 2885","children":[],"tail":"; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/182/tV/s501/f/8"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–182, title V, § 501(f)(8)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1996-08-06"},"text":"Aug. 6, 1996","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/110/1692"},"text":"110 Stat. 1692","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idb64ca41d-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idb64ca41e-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"idb64ca41f-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Consumer Product Safety Act, referred to in text, is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/92/573"},"text":"Pub. L. 92–573","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1972-10-27"},"text":"Oct. 27, 1972","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/86/1207"},"text":"86 Stat. 1207","children":[],"tail":", which is classified generally to chapter 47 (§ 2051 et seq.) of Title 15, Commerce and Trade. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s2051"},"text":"section 2051 of Title 15","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"idb64ca420-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1996—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/182"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–182","children":[],"tail":" made technical amendment to section catchline and first word of text."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
